{
  "texts": [
    "But there are differences to the AGI case.",
    "First, humans are not capable of disempowering humanity.",
    "Plausibly, some humans would indeed try to disempower humanity if they were capable of it (Carlsmith 2022, Sect. 4.2).",
    "However, some humans would not.",
    "How do we explain this?"
  ]
}